---
title: Roasted Chickpea and Bulgur Shrimp Salad with Mint and Feta
description: This vibrant salad is bursting with herbaceous goodness and will satisfy vegetarians and non-vegetarians alike! Fibre-dense chickpeas are roasted with spices to add extra oomph.

